         <abstract>
            <p>The nondefiniteness of the Kronrod extension of the Gauss-Gegenbauer integration rule with weight function $w(x; \mu) = (1 - x^2)^{\mu - 1/2}, 0 &lt; \mu &lt; 1$, is shown when there are more than three abscissas.</p>
          </abstract>
